{"tid":35823,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"自動波定棍波好？","createTime":"2016-12-12T10:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T14:26:42.000Z","uid":20570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf156b6300f955d05399c48ada64aab01183638","tid":35823,"uid":20570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"我想快d考完個牌去澳洲Working holiday揸<br />\n見到人考棍波 好似好難1 take pass<br />\n自動波就容易d 可以快d拎到個牌<br />\n但考完棍 就有兩個牌 好似抵屌<br />\n諗咗好耐 有冇巴打可以比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：揸棍波真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee05e15bd1022810fc93f40aaec33c2c421a882","tid":35823,"uid":47023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"外國棍波，香港算9數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ab3d78e8e05f4837edac5f3ed15d8f3428e22a","tid":35823,"uid":20570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外國棍波，香港算9數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覆得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁姐係自動波d？"},{"pid":"5bd56ad10ce169eb1c95faf8755673385564700b","tid":35823,"uid":20570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>外國棍波，香港算9數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覆得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁姐係自動波d？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a5b645b6af38117efa78c63290f7b5e5d76094","tid":35823,"uid":36791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"自動波最安全"},{"pi