ime":"2016-12-12T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>難d咪練多d囉<br />\n<br />\n你問我一定叫你考棍</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打 如果要考棍 報駕駛學院定其他<br />\n<br />\n利申：咩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101c1d96477fdac8615aafa155049c1212d1f459","tid":35823,"uid":48634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"係男人就考棍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自動波迫力比油邊個唔識呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f828ac98e01312086c9319d97d7c1327c2b956","tid":35823,"uid":20570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由P牌至攞國際牌 需時一年啵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我知 就想快d考個牌 等一年先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5a8a918c1c2884551bc467748ee12406a49e8e","tid":35823,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:02:55.000Z","msg":"自動最舒服<br />\n純粹代步就自動波<br />\n想享受揸車樂趣就棍波"},{"pid":"ee03f480418c45a866e952cdc0a1b4f3a4e973b2","tid":35823,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"棍就真係有機會fail嘅<br />\n自動波都無1 take pass就唔好考車<br />\n同埋自動波學嘅堂數都少d<br />\n咁你預返個期 萬一fail左趕唔切拎國際牌 <br />\n咁咪自動波穩陣d先囉<br />\n講真棍波係香港淨係渣私家車真係無撚用<br />\n<br />\nBtw 考左筆試未"},{"pid":"9f85a7883ed505d35ae6f317720aae735102b4a3","tid":35823,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"男人老狗 渣住個廢牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25318044a1f9b84d6118c4234fc209a71b453da2","tid":35823,"uid":57047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:09:49.000Z","msg":"如果棍波會驚手腳唔協調<br />\n都係唔好揸車啦"},{"pid":"d5cb6787f4aa14fa74fef9e48cd2d2267125669f","tid":35823,"uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"自動啦。<br />\n唔洗理咩廢唔廢牌。<br />\n現代人，緊係取易不取難，<br />\n除非你好鍾意車，否則講得廢牌嗰啲人全部都係未進化"},{"pid":"4119cdcac80e1062c1fb8bfefa8e8c003e907ade","tid":35823,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁如果考左自動先 遲下先再考棍 會唔會太on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會"},{"pid":"f603e5b9cbab23aac9c8033cde8906d9f5ffb6dc","tid":35823,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自動啦。<br />\n唔洗理咩廢唔廢牌。<br />\n現代人，緊係取易不取難，<br />\n除非你好鍾意車，否則講得廢牌嗰啲人全部都係未進化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n外國唔係好多有得租自動波車...<br />\n好似我去英國就得棍波....好彩都重記得點楂....<br />\n<br />\n係香港就算吧啦....自動波無咁麻煩 (但係棍仔係大力D 同省油D)"},{"pid":"b65891bd655ec12e2aff1a0e249ace8a02247a89","tid":35823,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"有無巴打知道澳洲果面棍皮定自皮主導？<br />\n感覺車係代步工具既國家既話，好多時都係棍皮主導，好多棍皮舊車咁<br />\n<br />\n利申: 鄉下仔未出城唔識野"},{"pid":"81a75bb8b92070b008d06b78d36021dec84ae368","tid":35823,"uid":430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"點解叫棍皮唔叫棍波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0486259e8ee37b8540ce17a4bc68aed8816062e","tid":35823,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"睇你咩心態姐<br />\n如果對車無咩興趣為方便既話，自動波就輕鬆好多<br />\n好似我對車無咩耐性，考棍個陣都覺得好麻煩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6387e142c434e5b67a1ed025dd0d305bfa785ae","tid":35823,"uid":20570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無巴打知道澳洲果面棍皮定自皮主導？<br />\n感覺車係代步工具既國家既話，好多時都係棍皮主導，好多棍皮舊車咁<br />\n<br />\n利申: 鄉下仔未出城唔識野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上網睇到澳洲自動波比較主導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553c1749b7a9d7de7b1728bbac57e2b99d0fa123","tid":35823,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"考棍波可以揸4種<br />\n用唔用係一回事<br />\n既然差唔多錢 點解唔揀個回報大少少？"},{"pid":"ef09b01c686d49581b07003e37eb826e56420c61","tid":35823,"uid":43833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自動最舒服<br />\n純粹代步就自動波<br />\n想享受揸車樂趣就棍波</blockquote><br />\nching講得好啱，自動波車只係工具，行前行後轉左轉右。<br />\n棍波車直頭係駕駛藝術，兩者根本唔同市場<br />\n<br />\n有信心一定係選12 van，由其是去working holiday有車牌搵工都易d"},{"pid":"f2fe5478199bf45a2b644da4f73f8d840d597e6d","tid":35823,"uid":14570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"去外國識揸棍係好事<br />\n利申棍 van 1 take pass"},{"pid":"1cb9cd0aafbd1aac98408a77d6e211256ccd7076","tid":35823,"uid":12523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T18:50:58.000Z","msg":"自動棍波"},{"pid":"b7acb595186dfb14f95340008b0f349034ebf9f8","tid":35823,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T19:24:15.000Z","msg":"考棍渣自"},{"pid":"a94d4ec61cc7cdd76a8a9930a2fe3bf59ee0f686","tid":35823,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"宜家有無新車得黎 要有尾  四門  棍波選擇？  50萬樓下 唔要掃把佬... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0feaf2e033887bd018074da2693117fdea956fd","tid":35823,"uid":47135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"去working vista 都係想食女<br />\n棍波+50分"},{"pid":"7682f1c95ed9e1ce5ebe599fa8a8aa8c9ce2c448","tid":35823,"uid":352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,