":35823,"uid":15435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"棍啦<br />\n到時租唔到自動你就大撚鑊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984f5b0bb98142d37e4b2ec5bec8e304bb6bf275","tid":35823,"uid":46785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:55:19.000Z","msg":"純代步就自動<br />\n對車有興趣就一定係棍，冇得傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e1677cf228abc5d7cb92ddde3d53be0fadadc5","tid":35823,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T17:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解叫棍皮唔叫棍波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解叫豬柳強唔叫豬柳蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff2b8a2ab2c35c13680bd6a83f57964038903fd","tid":35823,"uid":12523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家有無新車得黎 要有尾  四門  棍波選擇？  50萬樓下 唔要掃把佬... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵代理訂部棍s3<br />\nBmw都好似有得訂棍<br />\n如果hatch back選擇多d"},{"pid":"196c85b1ea09be20b6a7d458e035beb368f521a4","tid":35823,"uid":31089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考棍波可以揸4種<br />\n用唔用係一回事<br />\n既然差唔多錢 點解唔揀個回報大少少？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設<br />\n自動波pass rate係p<br />\n棍波pass rate係q (q&lt;p)<br />\n<br />\n第一次學成本係M<br />\n每次重考成本N<br />\n<br />\n自動波expected考牌成本 <br />\n= p*M + (1-p)p(M+N) + (M+2N)p(1-p)^2 + ...<br />\n= p[Sum(0toINF) (M+iN)(1-p)^i]<br />\n= p[M*Sum(0toINF) (1-p)^i + N*Sum(0toINF) i(1-p)^i]<br />\n= p[M/p + N(1-p)/p^2]<br />\n= M + N(1-p)/p<br />\n<br />\n棍波expected考牌成本<br />\n= q*M + (1-q)q(M+N) + (M+2N)q(1-q)^2 + ...<br />\n= q[Sum(0toINF) (M+iN)(1-q)^i]<br />\n= q[M*Sum(0toINF) (1-q)^i + N*Sum(0toINF) i(1-q)^i]<br />\n= q[M/q + N(1-q)/q^2]<br />\n= M + N(1-q)/q<br />\n<br />\n棍波expected - 自動波expected<br />\n= [M+N(1-q/q - M - N(1-p)/p]<br />\n= N*(1/q-1-1/p+1)<br />\n= N (1/q - 1/p)<br />\n&gt; 0<br />\n<br />\n棍波expected &gt; 自動波expected<br />\n用成本計考棍係貴過考自動波而唔係一樣<br />\n所以棍波return要高過自動波係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a6df37ad9c5d4c0d6878bced190a344ddfc6f0","tid":35823,"uid":27885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考棍波可以揸4種<br />\n用唔用係一回事<br />\n既然差唔多錢 點解唔揀個回報大少少？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假設<br />\n自動波pass rate係p<br />\n棍波pass rate係q (q&amp;lt;p)<br />\n<br />\n第一次學成本係M<br />\n每次重考成本N<br />\n<br />\n自動波expected考牌成本 <br />\n= p*M + (1-p)p(M+N) + (M+2N)p(1-p)^2 + ...<br />\n= p[Sum(0toINF) (M+iN)(1-p)^i]<br />\n= p[M*Sum(0toINF) (1-p)^i + N*Sum(0toINF) i(1-p)^i]<br />\n= p[M/p + N(1-p)/p^2]<br />\n= M + N(1-p)/p<br />\n<br />\n棍波expected考牌成本<br />\n= q*M + (1-q)q(M+N) + (M+2N)q(1-q)^2 + ...<br />\n= q[Sum(0toINF) (M+iN)(1-q)^i]<br />\n= q[M*Sum(0toINF) (1-q)^i + N*Sum(0toINF) i(1-q)^i]<br />\n= q[M/q + N(1-q)/q^2]<br />\n= M + N(1-q)/q<br />\n<br />\n棍波expected - 自動波expected<br />\n= [M+N(1-q/q - M - N(1-p)/p]<br />\n= N*(1/q-1-1/p+1)<br />\n= N (1/q - 1/p)<br />\n&amp;gt; 0<br />\n<br />\n棍波expected &amp;gt; 自動波expected<br />\n用成本計考棍係貴過考自動波而唔係一樣<br />\n所以棍波return要高過自動波係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ce9ce816096b4e4ba4bd77c0a981abadf606f878","tid":35823,"uid":43611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家有無新車得黎 要有尾  四門  棍波選擇？  50萬樓下 唔要掃把佬... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有尾好似得sti揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966d6f502661492f000bd8dc79339b38680d0262","tid":35823,"uid":41642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宜家有無新車得黎 要有尾  四門  棍波選擇？  50萬樓下 唔要掃把佬... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有尾好似得sti揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所有bmw都可以訂mt新車<br />\n不過500k樓下......"},{"pid":"71fbc7de2d8314fb84c8672ef9e118a2118daf05","tid":35823,"uid":10743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"當人地方肥棍波要萬幾考棍牌，可以揸到4隻車<br />\n你5000考個廢牌，揸得1隻車<br />\n邊個抵啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cadf81edbd0a7a9116660691a6aa445b62b641f","tid":35823,"uid":8546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁如果考左自動先 遲下先再考棍 會唔會太on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會啦，唔係搵食香港都好少機會揸到棍"}]}